"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-2024-04-16-team-canada-paris-olympics-gear-unveiled\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team Canada athletes will be outfitted by Lululemon at the 2024 Olympic and Paralympic Games in Paris this summer.\\u00c2  The gear the athletes will wear during the opening ceremony, podium, media appearances and closing ceremony was revealed by Lululemon on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9966275525050885, \"rank\": 0.0033208225530495642, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 42, \"end\": 51, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lululemon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\"}, {\"begin\": 76, \"end\": 92, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9995909576831074, \"rank\": 0.0004060525099595841, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 96, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999956435204, \"rank\": 4.356381238151672e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lululemon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The brand will outfit Team Canada for the second time in the Olympics and for the first time during the Summer Games.\\u00c2  Take a look.\\u00c2  This is the gear that Team Canada athletes will be wearing in Paris at the 2024 Olympics and Paralympics \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00a8\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00a6pic.twitter.com/LKoIV6q1Y0  Olympic and Paralympic athletes were involved in the design and testing process of the gear, allowing for more adaptable and customizable features to be incorporated.\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 285, \"end\": 296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9966275525050885, \"rank\": 0.0033208225530495642, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9966275525050885, \"rank\": 0.0033208225530495642, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 460, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999956435204, \"rank\": 4.356381238151672e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of those innovations include magnetic close zippers and more accessible pockets for Paralympians along with jackets and pants that can quickly convert to short sleeves and shorts in the warmer weather in Paris.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 915, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999956435204, \"rank\": 4.356381238151672e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tennis player Leylah Fernandez was among the athletes who revealed the red-and-white-emblazoned gear in Toronto on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 937, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leylah_Fernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leylah Fernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leylah_Fernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leylah_Fernandez\"}, {\"begin\": 1027, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 0.9999999644874158, \"rank\": 3.338135088857926e-08, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is most excited by how the gear represents Canada and the pride the athletes hold for their country.\\u00c2  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOnce I saw the kit, I was like, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Wow, this is it,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Fernandez told SI.\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1094, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9945830333866039, \"rank\": 0.005445829965669386, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHopefully we do well and hopefully we are able to bring back medals so that we can showcase this kit a lot more and just show that Canada is an awesome country.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2  Wheelchair rugby player Zak Madell was one of the Paralympians who helped test the gear for nearly two years and provided feedback on improvements to be made.\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1368, \"end\": 1374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9945830333866039, \"rank\": 0.005445829965669386, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheelchair_rugby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.891417374608596e-15, \"text\": \"Wheelchair rugby\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheelchair_rugby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wheelchair_rugby\"}, {\"begin\": 1427, \"end\": 1437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zak_Madell\", \"score\": 0.9999993827029443, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zak Madell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zak_Madell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zak_Madell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is most appreciative of the accessibility of the final product and how it fits on his body.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cA lot of thought, research, even insight from the Paralympic athletes went into this,\\\" Madell said.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Seeing our insight from the conversations I had a couple years ago really coming to fruition and seeing it as part of the kit has been a really good experience.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  It was important to the Lululemon team to include Madell and others to test the gear and create a collection that met the athletes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 needs.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lululemon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Lululemon chief product officer Sun Choe, that meant including small but meaningful details\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094like a fidget-spinner-type piece on the cord of a bucket hat or words of encouragement printed in text and braille on the inside of jackets to ease nerves that may arise.\\u00c2  Ultimately, the collection\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s designs\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094inspired by the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098City of Light \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094are reflective of efforts to make the Team Canada kit for the upcoming summer Games inclusive and adaptable throughout various situations to all who wear it.\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lululemon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\"}, {\"begin\": 2104, \"end\": 2107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Microsystems\", \"score\": 0.999975113687001, \"rank\": 2.0030556289224483e-05, \"text\": \"Sun\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Microsystems\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Microsystems\"}, {\"begin\": 2108, \"end\": 2112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_(Korean_surname)\", \"score\": 0.9955717364545229, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Choe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_(Korean_surname)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Choi_(Korean_surname)\"}, {\"begin\": 2457, \"end\": 2468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9966275525050885, \"rank\": 0.0033208225530495642, \"text\": \"Team Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo proud of what we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve been able to do to kind of solve the emotional pressure, as well as making sure that we had adaptable clothes that really worked for the Paralympians,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Choe said.\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The gear will be seen in action this summer when the athletes enter the opening ceremony in Paris on Friday, July 26 and throughout the Olympic and Paralympic Games.\\u00c2  Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2864, \"end\": 2869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999956435204, \"rank\": 4.356381238151672e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations    \\u00c2\\u00a9 2026ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 3110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Sports Illustrated or its affiliates, licensees and related brands.\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3405, \"entities\": [{\"beg